Mari menjadi teman saja.

29
00:02:48,168 --> 00:02:49,252
Baik.

30
00:02:53,757 --> 00:02:54,591
Apa?

31
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,014
Aku sangat peduli kepadamu.

32
00:03:01,473 --> 00:03:02,307
Aku menyukaimu.

33
00:03:05,977 --> 00:03:09,981
Maksudku, aku menyukaimu sebagai teman.
Benar, itu maksudku.

34
00:03:10,565 --> 00:03:13,068
Kau gadis hebat. Aku tak meragukannya.

35
00:03:13,527 --> 00:03:16,321
Aku akui, kadang kau tampak cantik.

36
00:03:17,614 --> 00:03:18,740
Tapi...

37
00:03:20,117 --> 00:03:23,078
Maksudku, bayangan kau jadi pacarku...
Terlihat...

38
00:03:24,579 --> 00:03:27,541
Agak aneh, 'kan?

39
00:03:27,624 --> 00:03:30,669
Kita sudah seperti keluarga, bukan?

40
00:03:38,260 --> 00:03:40,554
Terserah. Wajar tertawa dalam situasi ini.

41
00:03:41,596 --> 00:03:42,806
Silakan tertawa.

42
00:03:48,061 --> 00:03:50,731
Tapi tidak perlu berlebihan.
Aku tetap serius.

43
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:52,691
Tae-o.

44
00:03:55,277 --> 00:03:57,362
- Bukan kau.
- Apa?

45
00:03:57,446 --> 00:04:00,949
Pria yang aku maksud
di atas atap bukan kau.

46
00:04:05,746 --> 00:04:08,665
Tapi katamu dia membantu
mengatasi masalahmu,

47
00:04:08,749 --> 00:04:11,293
hingga akhirnya kau jatuh cinta kepadanya.

48
00:04:11,626 --> 00:04:13,545
Kau akan terus berbuat bodoh?

49
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:20,552
Jika bukan aku, lalu siapa? Katakan.

50
00:04:22,095 --> 00:04:26,266
Sebaiknya jujur saja jika ditolak.
Itu cara terbaik.

51
00:04:26,349 --> 00:04:28,185
Jujur tentang perasaanmu,

52
00:04:29,895 --> 00:04:30,979
dan melupakannya.

53
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:33,648
Sungguh bukan kau.

54
00:04:34,483 --> 00:04:35,817
Dia teman kerjaku.

55
00:04:37,152 --> 00:04:37,986
Teman kerja?

56
00:04:38,069 --> 00:04:40,906
Entah bagaimana
dia tahu tentang situasiku,

57
00:04:41,281 --> 00:04:43,742
jadi, aku agak merepotkan dia.

58
00:04:44,743 --> 00:04:47,746
Dia punya cara menghiburku
dan itu sangat membantuku.

59
00:04:48,205 --> 00:04:49,873
Hingga aku mulai suka dia.

60
00:04:50,415 --> 00:04:52,250
Mendadak suka. Aku sudah bilang, 'kan?

61
00:04:53,126 --> 00:04:55,879
Lalu bagaimana denganku?

62
00:04:56,171 --> 00:04:57,506
Aku menghiburmu juga, ya?

63
00:04:57,589 --> 00:05:01,218
Ada perbedaan besar antara pacar
dan teman yang menghiburku.

64
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:08,141
Ini pertama kalinya aku menyukai orang.

65
00:05:11,394 --> 00:05:14,898
Aku tak bisa menarik ucapanku,
tapi juga tak mau cerita lagi.

66
00:05:14,981 --> 00:05:16,274
Jadi, jangan tanya lagi.

67
00:05:21,196 --> 00:05:22,280
Sebentar.

68
00:05:25,033 --> 00:05:28,119
Jadi, aku baru saja kau tolak?

69
00:05:30,288 --> 00:05:31,206
Wah.

70
00:05:32,207 --> 00:05:33,959
Aku ditolak, padahal aku tak suka kau.

71
00:05:35,627 --> 00:05:37,671
Ini pengalaman baru. Terima kasih.

72
00:06:01,653 --> 00:06:02,487
Astaga.

73
00:06:05,198 --> 00:06:07,075
Ini yang terbaik.

74
00:06:08,118 --> 00:06:10,328
Bisa saja jadi lebih kikuk.

75
00:06:11,371 --> 00:06:13,248
Ini yang terbaik.

76
00:06:24,092 --> 00:06:27,512
<i>Pria yang aku maksud</i>
<i>di atas atap bukan kau.</i>

77
00:06:28,096 --> 00:06:31,391
Pria yang aku sukai sebenarnya bukan kau.

78
00:06:47,282 --> 00:06:50,827
Kenapa kau bisa begitu bodoh, Tae-o?

79
00:07:00,587 --> 00:07:03,465
<i>Sejujurnya,</i>
<i>aku takut persahabatan abadi kita</i>

80
00:07:04,049 --> 00:07:05,300
<i>akan berakhir.</i>

81
00:07:06,885 --> 00:07:08,887
<i>Aku berharap Song-i tak bilang,</i>

82
00:07:09,429 --> 00:07:10,805
<i>bahwa dia menyukaiku.</i>

83
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:13,183
<i>Tapi...</i>

84
00:07:14,017 --> 00:07:17,687
Ada perbedaan antara pacar
dan teman yang menghiburku.

85
00:07:18,772 --> 00:07:19,773
Astaga.

86
00:07:20,565 --> 00:07:22,025
Jadi, siapa pria itu?

87
00:07:52,514 --> 00:07:57,018
MENYATAKAN AKU MENYUKAIMU

88
00:08:01,272 --> 00:08:04,067
Aku suka suasananya.
Dari mana kau tahu tempat ini?

89
00:08:04,651 --> 00:08:06,152
Aku sering lewat sini.

90
00:08:07,946 --> 00:08:10,490
Aku ingin mengajak pacarku
ke tempat ini nanti.

91
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:23,378
Makan lagi.

92
00:08:23,878 --> 00:08:25,171
Baik.

93
00:08:28,425 --> 00:08:29,551
Kau tak minum bir?

94
00:08:30,427 --> 00:08:34,347
Biasanya minum, tapi kini bersamamu.
Salah satu tak boleh mabuk.

95
00:08:35,390 --> 00:08:36,933
Aku cuma minum sedikit.

96
00:08:38,309 --> 00:08:39,394
Terakhir kali,

97
00:08:40,061 --> 00:08:42,480
minum sedikit saja kau sudah mabuk.

98
00:08:45,358 --> 00:08:48,945
Ada seseorang yang aku suka.

99
00:08:50,488 --> 00:08:51,740
Awas!

100
00:09:05,545 --> 00:09:07,881
- Maaf.
- Minum perlahan. Mau tambah?

101
00:09:07,964 --> 00:09:09,966
Tidak. Ini cukup untukku.

102
00:09:10,383 --> 00:09:12,719
- Permisi.
- Sungguh, tak perlu.

103
00:09:15,847 --> 00:09:16,931
Maaf.

104
00:09:18,767 --> 00:09:19,934
Tak apa-apa.

105
00:09:25,815 --> 00:09:26,900
<i>Kini waktunya.</i>

106
00:09:28,943 --> 00:09:30,862
<i>Minta aku jadi pacarmu. Cepat.</i>

107
00:09:32,197 --> 00:09:33,198
Bisa dibantu?

108
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:37,410
- Bisa minta segelas bir lagi?
- Tentu.

109
00:09:47,337 --> 00:09:49,172
<i>Ini hari pertama kami jadi kekasih.</i>

110
00:09:49,923 --> 00:09:51,424
<i>Ini momen semacam itu.</i>

111
00:09:53,551 --> 00:09:54,385
Ada apa?

112
00:09:57,180 --> 00:09:58,264
Tak apa-apa.

113
00:10:10,777 --> 00:10:13,071
Sudah. Cobalah.

114
00:10:19,661 --> 00:10:20,954
Bagaimana?

115
00:10:21,538 --> 00:10:24,582
Ternyata ada banyak
makanan lezat di dunia!

116
00:10:25,917 --> 00:10:27,752
Makan perlahan. Awas tersedak.

117
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:30,213
Di mana Hun?

118
00:10:31,214 --> 00:10:32,590
Katanya tak mau makan.

119
00:10:32,674 --> 00:10:35,009
Dia di kamarnya seharian.

120
00:10:35,927 --> 00:10:39,055
Dia mestinya tak boleh terlalu berharap.

121
00:10:40,723 --> 00:10:42,350
Kalian makanlah.

122
00:10:45,937 --> 00:10:47,147
Kau juga? Kenapa?

123
00:10:47,522 --> 00:10:49,357
Aku tak berselera.

124
00:10:50,275 --> 00:10:53,403
Kenapa semua orang di rumah ini
jadi depresi?

125
00:11:04,330 --> 00:11:05,331
Biar aku bantu.

126
00:11:19,095 --> 00:11:20,096
Kau ditolak?

127
00:11:22,265 --> 00:11:23,641
Kau yang menolakku.

128
00:11:24,309 --> 00:11:26,769
Berhentilah meledekku.

129
00:11:37,906 --> 00:11:39,991
Kenapa? Dia bilang tak tertarik?

130
00:11:41,034 --> 00:11:42,202
Bukan begitu.

131
00:11:42,285 --> 00:11:43,411
Dia juga menyukaimu?

132
00:11:44,287 --> 00:11:48,082
Dia tak perlu mengatakannya.
Aku tahu dari yang aku rasakan.

133
00:11:48,666 --> 00:11:50,835
Lalu apa yang kau rasakan?

134
00:11:52,754 --> 00:11:54,589
Kurasa kami sedang pacaran.

135
00:11:55,965 --> 00:11:58,426
Apa? Kedengarannya kau tak terlalu yakin.

136
00:11:59,636 --> 00:12:02,055
Bukan semacam "ayo pura-pura kencan"?

137
00:12:03,723 --> 00:12:05,016
Kau tak menjelaskan

138
00:12:05,642 --> 00:12:09,145
perasaanmu dengan kata-kata.
Karena itu kau tak yakin.

139
00:12:09,479 --> 00:12:12,273
Astaga, berhentilah mengomel.

140
00:12:20,365 --> 00:12:22,992
Apa aku kurang menarik bagi kaum pria?

141
00:12:25,203 --> 00:12:26,913
Kenapa bilang begitu?

142
00:12:26,996 --> 00:12:29,791
Aku memang bercanda
bahwa kau menolakku.

143
00:12:30,041 --> 00:12:32,001
Tapi faktanya aku memang ditolak.

144
00:12:32,085 --> 00:12:33,461
Secara terang-terangan.

145
00:12:34,295 --> 00:12:37,340
Dengar, bagaimana masalah itu
disamakan dengan ini?

146
00:12:37,757 --> 00:12:42,512
Alasanku "menolakmu"
karena aku tak mau kehilangan teman.

147
00:12:43,137 --> 00:12:45,223
Astaga.

148
00:12:50,603 --> 00:12:53,398
Song-i, kau sungguh orang hebat.

149
00:12:53,481 --> 00:12:57,151
Mengerti? Kau cerdas, cerdik, dan lucu.

150
00:12:58,236 --> 00:13:01,281
Mayoritas orang akan berpikir
kau di atas rata-rata.

151
00:13:01,364 --> 00:13:04,617
Jadi, jangan pernah kehilangan
kepercayaan diri. Mengerti?

152
00:13:04,701 --> 00:13:06,953
Baiklah, lihat.

153
00:13:07,078 --> 00:13:10,123
Dekati dia dengan percaya diri,
tangan di saku.

154
00:13:10,206 --> 00:13:11,249
Katakan kepadanya...

155
00:13:12,834 --> 00:13:14,335
"Apa hakmu...

156
00:13:15,253 --> 00:13:16,587
"Apa hakmu...

157
00:13:16,713 --> 00:13:18,798
membuatku ragu?"

158
00:13:18,881 --> 00:13:23,052
Tepat. Angkat dagu, tatap dia
dengan pandangan merendahkan.

159
00:13:23,136 --> 00:13:25,346
Jangan ragu dan jangan mau direndahkan.

160
00:13:43,990 --> 00:13:45,992
Tapi entah apa ini akan berhasil.

161
00:13:46,326 --> 00:13:47,535
Karena kau jelek.

162
00:13:48,911 --> 00:13:51,247
- Hoi!
- Kaulah yang harus menolak dia.

163
00:13:52,206 --> 00:13:55,126
Tapi aku punya nasihat.

164
00:13:56,377 --> 00:13:58,296
Pria baik-baik tak akan membuat

165
00:13:58,588 --> 00:14:00,673
wanita yang dia cintai merasa ragu.

166
00:14:03,634 --> 00:14:04,927
Keren sekali.

167
00:14:08,848 --> 00:14:10,892
Tapi dia memang pria baik-baik.

168
00:14:11,893 --> 00:14:13,770
Kenapa membuatku merasa ragu?

169
00:14:26,699 --> 00:14:27,950
Kenapa serius sekali?

170
00:14:28,785 --> 00:14:29,786
Tugasmu?

171
00:14:30,119 --> 00:14:30,953
Sebentar.

172
00:14:34,916 --> 00:14:36,042
Kau menanyakan ini?

173
00:14:36,751 --> 00:14:38,169
Bisa dibilang tugas.

174
00:14:39,670 --> 00:14:40,630
Tugas cinta.

175
00:14:41,297 --> 00:14:42,256
Terserah.

176
00:14:43,424 --> 00:14:45,802
Omong-omong, bagaimana dengan gadis itu?

177
00:14:46,344 --> 00:14:47,553
Yang kau pikirkan.

178
00:14:49,138 --> 00:14:51,224
Kami sesekali bertemu.

179
00:14:53,935 --> 00:14:55,186
Jadi, kalian berkencan?

180
00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:57,063
Bukan begitu.

181
00:14:58,439 --> 00:15:00,149
Kami bertemu tiap ada kesempatan.

182
00:15:00,733 --> 00:15:01,776
Kami ke bioskop juga.

183
00:15:02,610 --> 00:15:03,694
Lancar.

184
00:15:03,778 --> 00:15:06,739
Cuma sesaat, ya?
Dia tak masalah dengan situasi ini?

185
00:15:09,575 --> 00:15:10,827
Haruskah aku tanyakan dia?

186
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:14,497
Kau tipe pemuda nakal, ya? Tak kuduga.

187
00:15:15,123 --> 00:15:16,040
Aku?

188
00:15:16,124 --> 00:15:19,127
Dia mungkin berpikir kau cuma main-main.

189
00:15:19,210 --> 00:15:22,296
Pura-pura kencan,
tapi bertindak selayaknya kekasih.

190
00:15:23,089 --> 00:15:25,591
Tunggu, rasanya aku pernah mengatakan ini.

191
00:15:28,261 --> 00:15:29,554
Benar. Song-i.

192
00:15:31,764 --> 00:15:33,724
Ingat ocehan Song-i saat mabuk

193
00:15:33,808 --> 00:15:35,685
tentang pemuda yang dia sukai?

194
00:15:36,269 --> 00:15:37,311
Kenapa?

195
00:15:37,728 --> 00:15:41,315
Dia pergi makan dan ke bioskop bersamanya.

196
00:15:43,317 --> 00:15:45,486
Tapi tampaknya tak banyak kemajuan.

197
00:15:45,903 --> 00:15:48,239
Mereka baru jumpa beberapa kali, 'kan?

198
00:15:48,322 --> 00:15:50,700
Di zaman ini, kecepatan sangat penting.

199
00:15:50,783 --> 00:15:53,411
Bertemu beberapa kali,
tapi tak ada perkembangan.

200
00:15:54,829 --> 00:15:57,290
Jelas pria itu hanya mempermainkannya.

201
00:15:57,874 --> 00:15:59,667
Bagaimana kau bisa yakin?

202
00:16:00,460 --> 00:16:02,253
Pikiran semua orang tak sama.

203
00:16:03,671 --> 00:16:05,465
Kenapa jadi tersinggung?

204
00:16:09,302 --> 00:16:10,303
Intinya, maksudku,

205
00:16:10,887 --> 00:16:13,139
dia merasa agak frustrasi.

206
00:16:13,848 --> 00:16:16,434
Gadis yang kau kencani
mungkin merasa sama.

207
00:16:17,143 --> 00:16:19,103
Mungkin kesal tapi tidak ditunjukkan.

208
00:16:21,189 --> 00:16:23,566
Apakah Song-i kesal?

209
00:16:23,649 --> 00:16:25,610
Entahlah. Nanti dia akan sadar

210
00:16:25,693 --> 00:16:28,446
tak semua pria sepertiku,
saat dia patah hati.

211
00:16:29,530 --> 00:16:32,116
Pria yang mempermainkan wanita
bukan orang baik-baik.

212
00:16:46,714 --> 00:16:49,050
- Mari aku bantu.
- Terima kasih.

213
00:16:52,053 --> 00:16:54,514
Ayo, kau sungguh butuh bantuan.

214
00:16:55,389 --> 00:16:57,141
Astaga.

215
00:17:03,898 --> 00:17:04,774
Selamat datang...

216
00:17:11,155 --> 00:17:11,989
Kenapa kemari?

217
00:17:12,073 --> 00:17:14,909
Aku hanya lewat
dan ada yang mau kukatakan.

218
00:17:15,826 --> 00:17:17,078
Kami boleh memesan?

219
00:17:17,161 --> 00:17:18,120
- Ya.
- Tentu.

220
00:17:18,246 --> 00:17:19,705
Aku saja.

221
00:17:26,045 --> 00:17:27,088
Ya.

222
00:17:27,964 --> 00:17:29,590
- Dia?
- Apa?

223
00:17:29,674 --> 00:17:32,051
Pria yang kau sukai, dia?

224
00:17:32,552 --> 00:17:34,512
- Dia sudah lulus SMU?
- Hoi.

225
00:17:34,804 --> 00:17:37,014
Jangan sok tahu. Mau bilang apa?

226
00:17:38,474 --> 00:17:40,851
Datanglah ke toko Do-hyeon sepulang kerja.

227
00:17:40,935 --> 00:17:41,978
Aku kirim alamatnya.

228
00:17:42,061 --> 00:17:44,814
Tentu. Tapi kenapa?

229
00:17:44,897 --> 00:17:48,067
Aku benci lihat Hun depresi,
aku mau belikan dia minuman.

230
00:17:50,069 --> 00:17:51,988
Jika bukan dia, lalu siapa?

231
00:17:52,071 --> 00:17:53,948
- Mungkin di dapur?
- Hoi!

232
00:17:55,449 --> 00:17:57,577
Song-i, bisa bantu di dapur?

233
00:17:57,660 --> 00:17:58,661
Segera!

234
