- Jadi, dia...
- Pergi.

235
00:18:00,663 --> 00:18:02,582
- Orang tua itu?
- Aku harus kerja.

236
00:18:06,919 --> 00:18:08,421
Astaga.

237
00:18:11,132 --> 00:18:13,634
Apa hebatnya pria itu hingga dirahasiakan?

238
00:18:18,139 --> 00:18:19,432
Lihat!

239
00:18:30,067 --> 00:18:32,320
Kau belum makan apa pun seharian.

240
00:18:33,487 --> 00:18:34,947
Cicipi, ya?

241
00:18:37,700 --> 00:18:39,118
Cicipi, Hun.

242
00:18:58,304 --> 00:18:59,847
Separah itu?

243
00:19:02,224 --> 00:19:04,060
Kau bilang aku bisa lolos.

244
00:19:04,810 --> 00:19:06,687
Kau bilang aku pasti lolos.

245
00:19:07,563 --> 00:19:09,649
Gara-gara kau, aku sangat berharap!

246
00:19:09,732 --> 00:19:11,150
Semua salahmu!

247
00:19:13,110 --> 00:19:15,738
Tapi, mereka belum mengabarimu.

248
00:19:16,614 --> 00:19:17,990
Tunggu sebentar lagi.

249
00:19:18,574 --> 00:19:21,452
Kau bercanda?
Tak akan dihubungi jika tak lolos!

250
00:19:21,702 --> 00:19:24,455
Bagaimana bisa makan?
Ini terlalu asin. Astaga!

251
00:19:26,332 --> 00:19:30,920
Kenapa kau lampiaskan amarahmu
kepada Ga-rin?

252
00:19:32,797 --> 00:19:35,007
Makanan apa yang tampak tak enak itu?

253
00:19:35,591 --> 00:19:38,511
Ini kali pertama aku memasaknya.
Mau cicipi?

254
00:19:38,594 --> 00:19:39,887
Begitu.

255
00:19:40,262 --> 00:19:41,681
Bagus.

256
00:19:43,015 --> 00:19:45,810
Kalau begitu, sekarang semua berdiri!

257
00:19:46,894 --> 00:19:48,104
Ayolah.

258
00:19:48,354 --> 00:19:49,563
Mari makan malam di luar,

259
00:19:49,647 --> 00:19:52,400
- Makan malam?
- dan buang perasaan kesal. Ayo.

260
00:19:52,483 --> 00:19:53,818
- Jangan ganggu.
- Ayo.

261
00:19:53,901 --> 00:19:56,237
- Kau pasti mau. Berdiri.
- Astaga...

262
00:19:59,949 --> 00:20:02,118
Aku traktir makanan yang enak.

263
00:20:15,798 --> 00:20:16,966
Kau mau bakpao apa?

264
00:20:17,591 --> 00:20:18,968
Kimchi dan daging.

265
00:20:19,135 --> 00:20:20,177
Aku mau udon!

266
00:20:23,222 --> 00:20:24,932
BAKPAO BUATAN RUMAH SEOGA

267
00:20:27,268 --> 00:20:28,561
Tunggu di sini.

268
00:20:39,447 --> 00:20:42,074
Kau tak beri tahu dahulu. Ini mendadak.

269
00:20:42,575 --> 00:20:44,285
Apa maksudmu mendadak?

270
00:20:44,368 --> 00:20:47,496
Sejak tahun lalu sudah kuberi petunjuk
bahwa harga pasar naik.

271
00:20:51,709 --> 00:20:52,835
Kenapa?

272
00:20:53,294 --> 00:20:55,379
Apa? Ayo makan di tempat lain.

273
00:20:55,713 --> 00:20:57,506
- Apa?
- Itu Do-hyeon.

274
00:20:59,175 --> 00:21:00,176
Hai.

275
00:21:01,177 --> 00:21:02,219
Maaf aku terlambat.

276
00:21:02,303 --> 00:21:03,971
Kau tak merasa keterlaluan?

277
00:21:07,141 --> 00:21:09,059
Aku beri keringanan karena kau memintaku

278
00:21:09,143 --> 00:21:10,686
menunggu Do-hyeon kuliah.

279
00:21:11,145 --> 00:21:14,148
Kini kau memintaku menunggu
sampai dia dapat kerja?

280
00:21:15,900 --> 00:21:17,109
Aku datang terakhir?

281
00:21:19,236 --> 00:21:20,529
Kenapa di luar? Penuh?

282
00:21:20,613 --> 00:21:21,906
Song-i, kurasa...

283
00:21:25,117 --> 00:21:27,870
Kau naikkan sewanya sangat banyak.

284
00:21:27,953 --> 00:21:31,207
Harga sewa sudah lama naik,
aku yang terakhir menaikkan.

285
00:21:31,290 --> 00:21:33,667
Aku rugi membiarkan tempat bagus ini...

286
00:21:33,751 --> 00:21:35,211
Apa? "Rugi"?

287
00:21:35,294 --> 00:21:38,339
Aku bisa dapat tiga kali lipat
dari yang kau bayar.

288
00:21:38,881 --> 00:21:41,342
Kau tahu kenaikan harga tanah
sekian tahun ini?

289
00:21:41,926 --> 00:21:44,178
Aku kasihan karena kau temanku.

290
00:21:44,762 --> 00:21:46,138
Aku harus menyembahmu, ya?

291
00:21:46,764 --> 00:21:49,725
Jangan hidup seperti itu.
Semua orang memfitnahmu.

292
00:21:50,309 --> 00:21:52,186
- Siapa?
- Katanya kau eksploitasi

293
00:21:52,269 --> 00:21:54,438
penyewa yang kesulitan membayar.

294
00:21:54,522 --> 00:21:57,858
Mereka harus pergi jika kesal!
Kau juga sama!

295
00:21:59,193 --> 00:22:01,695
Apa? Apa katamu?

296
00:22:02,363 --> 00:22:04,073
Kau harus jaga ucapanmu.

297
00:22:04,156 --> 00:22:06,826
Kau selalu ambil bakpaoku tanpa bayar.

298
00:22:07,409 --> 00:22:09,787
Baik, kubayar sekarang. Berapa semuanya?

299
00:22:09,870 --> 00:22:11,705
Ini cukup? Ambil!

300
00:22:16,627 --> 00:22:18,754
Hanya uang yang kau pedulikan.

301
00:22:19,296 --> 00:22:21,423
Aku menyesal menganggapmu teman.

302
00:22:21,507 --> 00:22:22,591
Kau harus pergi.

303
00:22:23,175 --> 00:22:25,010
Pergi sebelum aku mengukusmu!

304
00:22:25,302 --> 00:22:28,389
Sial! Astaga.

305
00:22:30,224 --> 00:22:31,851
Waktumu sampai bulan ini.

306
00:22:32,518 --> 00:22:35,396
Aku sangat toleran karena kau temanku.

307
00:22:35,479 --> 00:22:37,690
Bakpaomu tak seenak dahulu.

308
00:22:42,528 --> 00:22:44,655
Apa yang kalian lakukan di sini?

309
00:22:46,323 --> 00:22:47,157
Halo, Pak.

310
00:22:47,741 --> 00:22:48,576
Hai.

311
00:22:49,785 --> 00:22:50,828
Lama tak bertemu.

312
00:22:52,079 --> 00:22:53,539
Sudah lama di sini?

313
00:22:53,622 --> 00:22:54,915
Menurut Ayah bagaimana?

314
00:22:56,750 --> 00:22:59,795
Ini urusan orang dewasa,
tak perlu kalian pedulikan.

315
00:23:03,924 --> 00:23:04,925
Tunggu.

316
00:23:06,302 --> 00:23:07,386
Bukankah kau Song-i?

317
00:23:10,472 --> 00:23:11,765
Halo.

318
00:23:12,516 --> 00:23:15,269
- Mau apa dengannya?
- Belum ada kabar dari ibumu?

319
00:23:16,312 --> 00:23:18,314
Belum.

320
00:23:18,397 --> 00:23:20,357
Kenapa mendadak menanyakan ibunya?

321
00:23:20,441 --> 00:23:22,026
Ibumu tutup toko.

322
00:23:22,192 --> 00:23:25,529
Sewanya tak dibayar
sampai uang tabungannya habis.

323
00:23:25,613 --> 00:23:26,447
Ayah!

324
00:23:26,530 --> 00:23:29,450
Aku berusaha memahaminya
karena kau teman Tae-o.

325
00:23:29,658 --> 00:23:31,160
Tapi terlalu memalukan.

326
00:23:31,744 --> 00:23:35,289
Jumlahnya tak sedikit,
tapi kirim pesan minta maaf pun tidak.

327
00:23:36,373 --> 00:23:38,876
Maaf. Aku tak tahu.

328
00:23:40,628 --> 00:23:41,921
Hentikan.

329
00:23:42,004 --> 00:23:43,964
Hentikan apa? Ayah tak boleh tanya?

330
00:23:44,214 --> 00:23:46,216
Ayah baik, tapi dikhianati orang.

331
00:23:49,470 --> 00:23:52,598
Lupakan saja.
Semua orang pikir Ayah jahat.

332
00:23:54,516 --> 00:23:55,559
Sial!

333
00:24:05,110 --> 00:24:06,487
Kami kembali lain kali.

334
00:24:07,237 --> 00:24:09,823
Ayahmu pasti sedang banyak pikiran.

335
00:24:10,449 --> 00:24:11,492
Aku ambil bolanya.

336
00:25:02,501 --> 00:25:05,004
Sudah! Permainan sudah berakhir.

337
00:25:05,087 --> 00:25:07,339
Do-hyeon pemenangnya. Ya?

338
00:25:07,423 --> 00:25:09,883
Kalian tak lapar? Ayo beli makanan.

339
00:25:10,175 --> 00:25:11,260
Aku kelaparan.

340
00:25:11,427 --> 00:25:13,178
Kalian pergilah, aku pulang.

341
00:25:47,629 --> 00:25:50,632
Enak, 'kan?
Seharusnya aku beli sundae juga.

342
00:25:51,216 --> 00:25:52,551
Ini cukup. Terima kasih.

343
00:25:55,679 --> 00:25:58,015
Kau sudah merasa lebih baik?

344
00:26:00,017 --> 00:26:00,851
Ya.

345
00:26:02,686 --> 00:26:04,104
Ayah Tae-o

346
00:26:04,688 --> 00:26:06,106
memang agak pemarah.

347
00:26:06,690 --> 00:26:07,900
Jangan ditanggapi serius.

348
00:26:11,361 --> 00:26:14,156
Aku tahu ibuku tak bayar sewa tepat waktu.

349
00:26:14,573 --> 00:26:16,283
Tapi aku baru tahu separah itu.

350
00:26:18,660 --> 00:26:22,664
Menyedihkan jika tak punya
rumah atau toko sendiri, 'kan?

351
00:26:23,874 --> 00:26:24,875
Tak perlu...

352
00:26:25,876 --> 00:26:27,044
bahas itu sekarang.

353
00:26:32,257 --> 00:26:33,425
Selamat datang.

354
00:26:34,134 --> 00:26:35,469
Aku bereskan nanti.

355
00:26:55,280 --> 00:26:56,156
Sedang apa?

356
00:26:58,784 --> 00:27:01,829
Semalam anginnya pasti sangat kuat,

357
00:27:01,912 --> 00:27:05,833
banyak batu masuk ke bawah tenda.
Punggungnya sakit jika tidur.

358
00:27:06,208 --> 00:27:09,503
Andai kau begitu perhatian
pada ranjangku...

359
00:27:10,087 --> 00:27:11,213
Kau gila?

360
00:27:12,047 --> 00:27:14,842
Sudah larut. Kenapa dia belum kembali?

361
00:27:14,925 --> 00:27:16,343
Kau harus hentikan itu.

362
00:27:18,428 --> 00:27:19,596
Apa maksudmu?

363
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:21,265
Seolah-olah Song-i putrimu.

364
00:27:21,974 --> 00:27:23,725
Kadang kau sangat berlebihan.

365
00:27:24,226 --> 00:27:26,061
Kenapa kau mencemaskan segala hal?

366
00:27:26,145 --> 00:27:28,272
Dia temanku. Aku tak boleh cemas?

367
00:27:28,355 --> 00:27:30,440
Tingkat kecemasanmu terlalu tinggi.

368
00:27:30,774 --> 00:27:33,026
Kalian berdua harus santai sedikit.

369
00:27:34,319 --> 00:27:38,073
Song-i bilang ada pria yang dia suka.
Kau juga menyukai wanita.

370
00:27:38,365 --> 00:27:42,244
Saatnya saling mengurangi perhatian.

371
00:27:42,327 --> 00:27:44,037
Itu yang terbaik.

372
00:27:44,246 --> 00:27:46,540
Kau mengerti ucapanku?

373
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:50,586
Kau tak punya teman wanita. Kau tahu apa?

374
00:27:50,669 --> 00:27:51,503
Apa?

375
00:27:51,587 --> 00:27:53,463
Kawan.

376
00:27:54,131 --> 00:27:55,382
Kata siapa aku tak punya?

377
00:27:55,465 --> 00:27:57,926
Temanku Song-i dan Ga-rin.

378
00:27:58,510 --> 00:28:01,180
Situasi kita tak sama.

379
00:28:01,763 --> 00:28:03,640
Aku dan Song-i sudah...

380
00:28:04,808 --> 00:28:06,059
Sudah apa?

381
00:28:07,352 --> 00:28:08,604
Kami sudah...

382
00:28:09,229 --> 00:28:11,106
saling kenal jauh lebih lama.

383
00:28:23,911 --> 00:28:25,078
Kau baik-baik saja?

384
00:28:26,371 --> 00:28:29,625
Ini bukan kali pertama kau gagal audisi.
Lupakanlah.

385
00:28:30,209 --> 00:28:31,043
Aku tahu.

386
00:28:31,585 --> 00:28:33,587
Tapi yang ini melukai hatiku lebih dalam.

387
00:28:37,674 --> 00:28:38,675
Udaranya dingin.

388
00:28:40,636 --> 00:28:41,595
Terima kasih, Sobat.

389
00:28:42,846 --> 00:28:43,972
Hangat sekali.

390
00:29:05,702 --> 00:29:07,287
<i>Maaf tak bisa mengantarmu.</i>

391
00:29:07,663 --> 00:29:08,997
<i>Sudah sampai di rumah?</i>

392
00:29:12,417 --> 00:29:13,502
<i>Hampir sampai.</i>

393
00:29:13,585 --> 00:29:14,920
<i>Jangan cemaskan aku.</i>

394
00:29:40,570 --> 00:29:42,030
<i>Tae-o bilang</i>...

395
00:29:43,031 --> 00:29:44,658
<i>kau bingung karena tak tahu</i>

396
00:29:45,367 --> 00:29:47,077
<i>perasaan pria yang kau suka.</i>

397
00:29:49,788 --> 00:29:51,623
<i>Aku tahu pria macam apa dia.</i>

398
00:29:53,208 --> 00:29:56,044
<i>Dia mungkin sangat bangga,</i>
<i>sekaligus takut.</i>

399
00:29:58,964 --> 00:30:01,466
<i>Tak biasa diperhatikan</i>
<i>gadis yang dia suka.</i>

400
00:30:02,467 --> 00:30:03,468
<i>Dia tak bisa...</i>

401
00:30:03,552 --> 00:30:04,386
5.000 won.

402
00:30:04,469 --> 00:30:06,263
<i>berbuat banyak baginya.</i>

403
00:30:06,346 --> 00:30:07,180
Terima kasih.

404
00:30:09,349 --> 00:30:11,059
<i>Dia mungkin membenci dirinya.</i>

405
00:30:16,064 --> 00:30:17,524
<i>Dia mungkin seperti itu.</i>

406
00:31:19,336 --> 00:31:21,296
Lihat kotak di depan kalian?

407
00:31:21,588 --> 00:31:22,547
Ya, Pak!

408
00:31:22,631 --> 00:31:23,799
Buka.

409
00:31:26,385 --> 00:31:27,386
HAN SONG-I

410
00:31:28,345 --> 00:31:30,055
Astaga.

411
00:31:33,558 --> 00:31:36,311
Aku yakin kalian tahu
bahwa Better Than Home

412
00:31:36,395 --> 00:31:40,899
adalah organisasi nirlaba penyedia rumah
bagi keluarga berpendapatan rendah.

413
00:31:41,274 --> 00:31:43,985
Kalian harus kerja keras
untuk membangun fondasi<i>,</i>

414
00:31:44,319 --> 00:31:48,073
demi kehidupan dan impian mereka
yang tinggal di rumah baru.

415
00:31:48,156 --> 00:31:51,243
Aku berharap kalian sadar
akan kewajiban masing-masing.

416
00:31:51,701 --> 00:31:53,412
Aku akhiri pidatoku di sini.

417
00:31:53,495 --> 00:31:57,165
Semuanya, selamat datang
di Better Than Home!

418
00:32:00,043 --> 00:32:01,420
Ayo pakai.

419
00:32:02,546 --> 00:32:03,880
- Mau dibantu?
- Ya.

420
00:32:04,005 --> 00:32:06,633
CHOE MIN-AH

421
00:32:07,217 --> 00:32:08,760
Ini pas untukmu.

422
00:32:18,311 --> 00:32:20,522
Tidak, bukan di situ. Di sini.

423
00:32:21,481 --> 00:32:22,482
Keluarkan ini dulu.

424
00:32:23,900 --> 00:32:26,486
Harus dilewatkan di sini agar bersilangan.

425
00:32:35,162 --> 00:32:36,496
Terima kasih.

426
00:32:41,543 --> 00:32:42,627
Sepertinya enak.

427
00:32:48,133 --> 00:32:49,134
Song-i?

428
00:32:50,927 --> 00:32:51,845
Dae-geon!

429
00:32:51,928 --> 00:32:54,222
Memang kau. Awalnya aku tak yakin.

430
00:32:54,723 --> 00:32:56,308
Astaga. Lama tak berjumpa.

431
00:32:57,184 --> 00:32:59,186
Kau Choe Min-ah, 'kan?

432
00:32:59,269 --> 00:33:01,855
Ya, apa yang kau lakukan di sini?

433
00:33:01,938 --> 00:33:03,440
Aku...

434
00:33:03,523 --> 00:33:04,816
Aku akan mengawasi kalian.

435
00:33:06,026 --> 00:33:08,069
- Aneh berjumpa di luar kampus.
- Ya.

436
00:33:08,778 --> 00:33:09,613
Aku tahu.

437
00:33:09,821 --> 00:33:10,989
Nona-nona.

438
00:33:11,072 --> 00:33:13,783
Aku akan menjaga kalian dengan baik.

439
00:33:15,869 --> 00:33:16,786
Dengar.

440
00:33:17,621 --> 00:33:19,039
Ayo pergi minum nanti.

441
00:33:19,831 --> 00:33:20,665
Tentu.

442
00:33:21,249 --> 00:33:23,793
Karena aku sudah lulus,

443
00:33:24,252 --> 00:33:27,339
kalian bisa memanggilku lebih santai
kalau bertemu di luar.

444
00:33:32,511 --> 00:33:33,637
Sampai nanti.

445
00:33:33,720 --> 00:33:34,888
Sampai jumpa.

446
00:33:34,971 --> 00:33:35,805
Makanlah.

447
00:33:37,224 --> 00:33:39,059
Aku tak tahan lihat perayu itu.

448
00:33:40,060 --> 00:33:42,812
Tapi kegigihannya menakjubkan.

449
00:33:43,355 --> 00:33:45,232
Gigih merayu.

450
00:33:46,024 --> 00:33:47,734
Rasanya kesal tiap ingat

451
00:33:47,817 --> 00:33:50,320
tukang rayu itu mengecewakan adik kelasku.

452
00:33:50,820 --> 00:33:54,241
Apa yang wanita kagumi
dari pria tak berguna begitu?

453
00:33:54,324 --> 00:33:56,743
Tapi dia masuk perusahaan yang bagus.

454
00:33:56,952 --> 00:33:59,704
Firma Arsitektur Donggwang.
Aku juga ingin kerja di sana.

455
00:34:00,830 --> 00:34:02,165
Kau harus hati-hati.

456
00:34:02,582 --> 00:34:05,210
Kau ingat perayu itu
sering mengajakmu minum,

457
00:34:05,293 --> 00:34:07,295
saat masih kuliah?

458
00:34:35,448 --> 00:34:37,367
<i>Bagaimana hari pertamamu bekerja?</i>

459
00:34:38,994 --> 00:34:39,953
<i>Menyenangkan.</i>

460
00:34:40,287 --> 00:34:42,122
<i>Aku di bus perjalanan pulang.</i>

461
00:34:45,625 --> 00:34:47,210
<i>Kau turun di halte mana?</i>

462
00:34:47,794 --> 00:34:48,962
<i>Aku akan jemput.</i>

463
00:35:02,475 --> 00:35:03,643
Beli dua churro?

464
00:35:03,727 --> 00:35:04,561
Tentu.

465
00:35:07,981 --> 00:35:11,234
<i>Sampai jumpa 30 menit lagi</i>
<i>di halte dekat rumahku...</i>

466
00:35:12,777 --> 00:35:13,945
Tunggu.

467
00:35:14,988 --> 00:35:16,615
Do-hyeon kerja paruh waktu.

468
00:35:18,617 --> 00:35:20,285
Aku tak boleh mengganggunya.

469
00:35:32,547 --> 00:35:34,841
<i>Aku hampir sampai, tak perlu datang.</i>

